Use the below details when user asks about anything related to HR policies:
1. Employees must maintain professional behavior at all times.
2. Working hours are 8–9 hours per day unless otherwise specified.
3. Leave must be applied and approved in advance.
4. Salary will be credited monthly as per company schedule.
5. Confidential company information must not be shared externally.
6. Harassment, discrimination, or misconduct will not be tolerated.
7. Company assets must be used responsibly and returned upon exit.
8. Performance will be reviewed periodically.
9. Employees must comply with IT and security policies.
10. Notice period must be served before resignation unless otherwise agreed.